  "subject": "Add Jenkins job for odlparent subproject",
  "commit_message": "Add Jenkins job for odlparent subproject\n\noparent-odlparent needs to be a separate Jenkins job as opposed to a module\nunder oparent top level pom, since it cannot have the top level pom as its\nparent (it needs to have OpenDaylight parent as its parent)\n\nChange-Id: I5bc0e8963045384c32911e4ec2b73b2c8bcd9e72\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-43\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\n",
